{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773180/extras/gifCross620opti.gif?t=1728569135\" /><br><br>From 2 to 8 players, The Matriarch is a deadly hide &amp; seek party game where everyone is an imposter. It mixes social guessing with hide-and-seek mechanics and causes Paranoia in all players involved!  <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773180/extras/theBots.png?t=1728569135\" /><br>BOTs are just programmed to complete their tasks, from milking cows to harvesting potatoes, they don't question the Matriarch's orders! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773180/extras/TheSinners.png?t=1728569135\" /><br><strong>Goal: Hide from the Matriarch and find the exit </strong><br>They look like BOTs but are controlled by real players.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Emulate the BOTs to avoid drawing attention to yourself, when the Matriarch is around. <br></li><li>Wait for the right opportunity to go underground.<br></li><li>Dig to find the path that will lead you to the exit. <br></li><li>Pray that the Matriarch doesn't have you in her radar when the night comes.</li></ul> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773180/extras/thematriarch.png?t=1728569135\" /><br><strong>Goal: Identify and Sacrifice all the Sinners </strong><br>Also controlled by a player. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Patrol the convent and observe the Nuns<br></li><li>Keep track of those with suspicious behavior...<br></li><li>...or be unpredictable and catch them off guard<br></li><li>Identify and Sacrifice the Sinners</li></ul><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Customize your games: Experiment with different maps, rounds length, random Matriarch, and more! <br></li><li> Unlock new sacrifice devices: Giant cross, Guillotine, Pyre, Venomous Snakes...the choice is yours! <br></li><li> Play on public servers and meet new players, or open up your own private server and play with a group of friends.<br></li><li> Enjoy free updates that bring more maps and customization options!</li></ul><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773180/extras/SteamWishlistFollowGIF_FF_HighV3.gif?t=1728569135\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Burn them all! ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1773180/930b1a1870b9e9a57858ff78b1fe3e02400c8e51.jpg"},{"name":"Off with his head!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1773180/6890a351907411a81ac6422701455f65b1ad3ee2.jpg"},{"name":"We will survive! ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1773180/1632b0c319276d78d6ab049c1131dea93d08f991.jpg"},{"name":"Strike! ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1773180/17a5819a8de6e6390e6a65e6e6af9f9d8c5c8bde.jpg"},{"name":"No mistakes were made","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1773180/5ba245eaea657f0538096f468dd6f9fff5f495e6.jpg"},{"name":"Mephistopheles","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1773180/51396498a2ef5b425bd7a4d277963785bf645514.jpg"},{"name":"Escape now, hug later.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1773180/074796fe550fb2302ff5573e07f3298e698ba1ab.jpg"},{"name":"Last woman standing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1773180/2dccbed361e907081a8ba1962c6f2f1df5c4b88e.jpg"},{"name":"The Prisoner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1773180/a82ff1197bf4a601d17f9b182b89491d87941f31.jpg"},{"name":"Gold Digger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/